---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Intellectual Property & Trademark Licensing Policy" description="Behold Your Wonder intellectual property, trademark, and licensing policy.">
  <div class="legal-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span style="font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:500;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#C4917A;display:block;margin-bottom:12px;">Legal</span>
      <h1 style="color:#F5EFE8;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);margin:12px 0;">Intellectual Property &amp; Trademark Licensing Policy</h1>
      <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);font-size:0.9rem;">Effective Date: June 2026</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="legal-body">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="legal-content">

        <h2>Ownership of Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>Behold Your Wonder® and all associated logos, branding, trade dress, and visual identity are the intellectual property of Salatha Helton, LMFT. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>Core Messaging Based Therapy™ (CMBT™), the Behold Your Wonder Center for Core Messaging Based Therapy™, and all related frameworks, methodologies, training materials, worksheets, and written works are jointly owned by Salatha Helton, LMFT. All rights reserved.</p>

        <h2>Registered and Pending Trademarks</h2>
        <p>The following marks are registered or pending registration with the United States Patent and Trademark Office (USPTO):</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Behold Your Wonder® — registered trademark</li>
          <li>Core Messaging Based Therapy™ (CMBT™) — trademark pending</li>
          <li>Behold Your Wonder Center Core Messaging Based Therapy™ — trademark pending</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Unauthorized use of these marks in commerce, in connection with therapeutic services, educational content, or clinical training materials is prohibited without prior written authorization.</p>

        <h2>Permitted Use</h2>
        <p>Referential use of the above marks — for example, in academic citation, journalism, or factual description — is permitted provided that such use does not suggest affiliation, endorsement, or sponsorship by Behold Your Wonder or its owners, and that trademark symbols are included where applicable.</p>

        <h2>Licensing</h2>
        <p>Behold Your Wonder does not currently offer public licensing of the CMBT™ framework, methodology, or training materials. Clinicians, training programs, and organizations interested in licensing inquiries should contact us directly at the address below. Licensing requests are evaluated on a case-by-case basis and are subject to formal written agreement.</p>

        <h2>Copyright</h2>
        <p>All written content published on this website — including journal articles, clinical descriptions, service descriptions, and educational materials — is protected by copyright. © 2026 Behold Your Wonder Counseling & Consulting, Inc. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        <p>Reproduction, distribution, or adaptation of any content from this site without prior written permission is prohibited. Quotes of reasonable length for the purposes of commentary, criticism, or education are permitted provided full attribution is given.</p>

        <h2>Infringement</h2>
        <p>Behold Your Wonder actively monitors for unauthorized use of its intellectual property. If you believe your intellectual property has been infringed upon by content on this site, or if you wish to report unauthorized use of Behold Your Wonder intellectual property, please contact us.</p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p><strong>Behold Your Wonder Counseling & Consulting, Inc.</strong><br>
        Email: legal@beholdyourwonder.com</p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-hero { background: #1E2D1E; padding: 80px 0; text-align: center; }
  .legal-body { background: #F5EFE8; padding: 80px 0; }
  .legal-content { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #1E2D1E; }
  :global(.legal-content h2) { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.6rem; color: #1E2D1E; margin: 48px 0 16px; }
  :global(.legal-content p) { margin-bottom: 20px; }
  :global(.legal-content ul) { padding-left: 24px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  :global(.legal-content li) { margin-bottom: 8px; }
  :global(.legal-content a) { color: #C4917A; text-decoration: underline; }
</style>